.TH combat
.SH NAME
combat-req
.SH DESCRIPTION
The combat requirement specifies if the object should be engaged in combat or not.
.SH PARAMETERS
.P
* combat
.br
Specifies specifies whether object need to be in combat("true") or not("false").
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<reqs>
	<combat-req combat="true"/>
</reqs>
.SH SEE ALSO
requirements